---
interface Ticket {
  code: string;
  mode: string;
  route: string;
  summary: string;
  detail: string;
}

interface Props {
  assetHref: string;
  ticket: Ticket;
}

const { assetHref, ticket } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="nordic-hero" data-cinematic-reveal>
  <div class="nordic-film-edge nordic-film-edge--top" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="nordic-film-edge nordic-film-edge--bottom" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="nordic-map-panel">
    <span class="nordic-map-panel__tape" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <div class="nordic-map-panel__heading">
      <span>Nordic</span>
      <span>Field Notes</span>
      <small>59°N–69°N / Route Draft 02</small>
    </div>
    <div class="nordic-rec" aria-hidden="true"><span></span> REC</div>
    <time class="nordic-timecode" aria-hidden="true">00:00:18</time>

    <div class="nordic-map-panel__camera">
      <img
        class="nordic-map-panel__image"
        src={assetHref}
        alt="依据真实国界和城市坐标绘制的北欧路线图，包含 Stockholm、Oslo、Bergen、Helsinki 和 Tromsø"
        width="760"
        height="760"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />

      <svg class="nordic-map-active" viewBox="0 0 760 760" aria-hidden="true">
        <path class="nordic-map-active__route" data-nordic-route d="" hidden></path>
        <circle class="nordic-map-active__point" data-nordic-origin cx="393.3" cy="549.3" r="7" hidden></circle>
        <circle class="nordic-map-active__point is-arriving" data-nordic-destination cx="393.3" cy="549.3" r="8"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <p class="nordic-map-panel__note">
      主线只走 Stockholm → Oslo → Bergen。Helsinki 与 Tromsø 留作片尾延伸，按季节和总天数接入。
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="nordic-intro">
    <div class="nordic-intro__slate">
      <p class="nordic-eyebrow">A Film Before Departure · 2026</p>
      <span aria-hidden="true">TAKE 01 / NORTHBOUND</span>
    </div>
    <h1>北欧五日</h1>
    <p class="nordic-intro__context">从斯德哥尔摩出发</p>
    <p class="nordic-intro__dek">
      一部尚未开拍的旅行短片。先把铁路、峡湾、城市与返程缓冲写进分镜，再等待真正的出发日期。
    </p>

    <dl class="nordic-stats">
      <div><dt>05</dt><dd>main days</dd></div>
      <div><dt>03</dt><dd>core cities</dd></div>
      <div><dt>02</dt><dd>extensions</dd></div>
    </dl>

    <aside class="nordic-ticket" data-nordic-ticket aria-live="polite">
      <div class="nordic-ticket__notch" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="nordic-ticket__head">
        <span data-ticket-code>{ticket.code}</span>
        <span data-ticket-mode>{ticket.mode}</span>
      </div>
      <p class="nordic-ticket__route" data-ticket-route>{ticket.route}</p>
      <p class="nordic-ticket__summary" data-ticket-summary>{ticket.summary}</p>
      <p class="nordic-ticket__detail" data-ticket-detail>{ticket.detail}</p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="nordic-opening-credits" aria-hidden="true">
  <span>Directed by weather & rail</span>
  <span>Scroll to begin ↓</span>
</div>
